    "extract": "Edwards Lifesciences Corporation is an American medical technology company headquartered in Irvine, California, specializing in tissue heart valves and transcatheter technologies for the treatment of structural heart disease. The company has manufacturing facilities at the Irvine headquarters, as well as in Draper, Utah; Costa Rica; Singapore; and Limerick, Ireland. The company is also constructing a manufacturing plant in Moncada, near Valencia, Spain, with a €150 million investment. Production is scheduled to begin in 2027."
